the first Crank film, top assassin Chev Chelios 
(Jason Statham) returns in this action-packed sequel 
to track down a ruthless Chinese mobster who has

the talented hit man scours Los Angeles for his 
enemy, he must continually jolt the mechanical 
ticker that beats within his chest -- otherwise, 
he's dead. Amy Smart and Dwight Yoakam co-star.
